---
interface Props {
  items: { label: string; plain: string }[];
  remedyHref: string; // e.g. /r/ashwagandha — the evidence grade
}
const { items, remedyHref } = Astro.props;
---

<section class="legend" aria-labelledby="legend-title">
  <h2 class="legend-title" id="legend-title">What the six ratings mean</h2>
  <p class="legend-sub">In plain words. Every product is scored 0–5 on each — more filled bars is better.</p>
  <dl class="legend-grid">
    {items.map((r) => (
      <div class="legend-item">
        <dt>{r.label}</dt>
        <dd>{r.plain}</dd>
      </div>
    ))}
  </dl>
  <p class="legend-foot">
    To make the page quick to read, we group the products into four <strong>trust tiers</strong> below —
    a shorthand for how well-sourced and transparent each is, drawn straight from these six scores.
    <strong>A tier is about how much you can trust what’s on the label — not whether you should buy it or
    whether it works for you</strong> (that’s the <a href={remedyHref}>evidence grade</a>). Tap
    “Why these scores” on any card for the specifics.
  </p>
</section>

<style>
  .legend {
    margin: 0 0 var(--sp-8);
  }
  .legend-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    line-height: var(--lh-2xl);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-tight);
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0 0 var(--sp-2);
  }
  .legend-sub {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: var(--lh-sm);
    color: var(--muted);
    margin: 0 0 var(--sp-6);
  }
  .legend-grid {
    margin: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--sp-6) var(--sp-8);
  }
  .legend-item {
    padding-top: var(--sp-4);
    border-top: var(--border-hairline);
  }
  .legend-item dt {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0 0 var(--sp-2);
  }
  .legend-item dd {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: var(--lh-md);
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .legend-foot {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: var(--lh-md);
    color: var(--muted);
    margin: var(--sp-6) 0 0;
    padding-top: var(--sp-5);
    border-top: var(--border-hairline);
    max-width: 74ch;
  }
  .legend-foot a {
    color: var(--primary);
  }
  .legend-foot strong {
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .legend-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
